                    <span>  Film includes many sexual scenes, female nudity and full frontal male nudity.
<br />Joe (Ewan McGregor) finds a dead woman floating towards the pier in the water.  his co-worker Les (Peter Mullan) do the right thing and call the police.  Joe lives with Les' family on the Atlantic Eve barge.  One night he notices through a crack in the wall that Les and his wife, Ella (Tilda Swinton) are hovaing sexual problems.  The next day while les is reading the newspaper at the table, Joe puts his leg onto Ella's under the table and makes a sexual motion with his hand.  She stops him. That night, while the husband is playing darts at a pub, Joe makes advances to Ella again in the barge.  She tells him firmly she does not want to awaken the boy.  They go outside on land and commit adultery.
<br />  Joe remembers Cathie (Emily Mortimer) who he had a sexual relationship with.
<br />  Joe and Ella are being oh so carefree about having sex while les is up on deckk, not knowing what goes on below.
<br />  Some strange turn of events are about to take place.
<br />  DVD includes in "Special Features", an extended sex scene, original passage narrations by Ewan McGregor, and two audio commentaries.
<br />  Good for you Ewan McGregor for being so brave la natural.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Cold Sex in Scotland</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
